Investment proﬁle








SECTORS


SECTORS
We invest in franchisors.  Segments of particular interest include restaurants (all formats), wellness and beauty, education, and healthcare. However, brands with exceptional products/services and strong unit economics, regardless of sector, are always of interest.





STAGE 


STAGE 
We seek brands that have achieved proof of concept. Delineators include superior unit economics, geographic diversity, and franchisee success.








SIZE


SIZE
Our fund seeks to make equity investments from $3MM up to $25MM.










